      <item>
        <title>Getting jekyll, surge etc to work on Windows Linux Subsystem</title>
        <description>&lt;h2&gt;Pontifications&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;have to re-compile ruby from scratch otherwise jekyll gem won&amp;#39;t build, no idea why :-)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;apt-get update &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-y&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;apt-get upgrade &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-y&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;apt-get &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-y&lt;/span&gt; build-essential ruby-full
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;gem update &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;--system&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;gem &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;jekyll bundler
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;gem &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;github-pages
apt-get &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;zlib1g-dev
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;apt-get &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;zlib1g-dev
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;gem &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;github-pages &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# don't need this&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;gem &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;redcarpet
curl &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-sL&lt;/span&gt; https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_8.x | &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-E&lt;/span&gt; bash -
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;apt-get &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-y&lt;/span&gt; nodejs 
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;sudo &lt;/span&gt;npm &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;--global&lt;/span&gt; surge
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
