      <item>
        <title>Moving blogging to old MacBook Air in preparation for move to new Windows Machine</title>
        <description>&lt;h2&gt;Pontifications&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First I had to install ruby:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;brew upgrade rbenv ruby-build
rbenv &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;2.5.0
rbenv global 2.5.0
vi ~/.bash_profile &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# and add eval &quot;$(rbenv init -)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
